* create a "bunch-of-tests-list by URI" handler, accepting various kind of source : csv file, etc. Each URI should have its own bunch of tests.
* create a list of the available bunch of tests
* create a runcronjob.php to be launched via the crontab, processing the tests & sending an email to a per-URI receivers list
* create a web version, that could be based on the Apache Zeta Components MvcTools
  see http://incubator.apache.org/zetacomponents/documentation/trunk/MvcTools/tutorial.html
